\":30}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"toolu_bdrk_013yNHpJsZNzA5X7FuVGaGzm\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"path\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/gitlab-mr/SKILL.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"museai\",\"model\":\"mihoyo.claude-4-6-opus\",\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773777654551},{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"toolu_bdrk_01FWPQgDuhkZQLB8BydCxJwy\",\"toolName\":\"exec\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"From platgit.mihoyo.com:plat/oa/im/pc/wave-openclaw-wrapper\\n - [deleted]         (none)     -> origin/bot/im_md/feat/auto-bugfix-phase1_5\\n - [deleted]         (none)     -> origin/bot/xiaogang-bot/feat/session-reflection\\n - [deleted]         (none)     -> origin/fix/improve-pm2-port-cleanup-20260317\\n - [deleted]         (none)     -> origin/pp/xg/prune_presets\\n   88e1ed5..f7e6781  main       -> origin/main\\n---BRANCHES---\\norigin/bot/im_md/feat/daily-tasks-skill 2 days ago wave前端龙虾\\norigin/bot/xiaogang-bot/feat/deploy-notify 4 days ago wave前端龙虾\\norigin/bot/im_md/feat/morning-standup-report 5 days ago wave前端龙虾\\norigin/bot/im_md/docs/req004-bugid-dimension 7 days ago wave前端龙虾\\norigin/bot/xiaogang-bot/docs/req-005-auto-cleanup 7 days ago wave前端龙虾\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1773777676305},{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"toolu_bdrk_013yNHpJsZNzA5X7FuVGaGzm\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"---\\nname: gitlab-mr\\ndescription: Manage GitLab merge requests for stellar-fe or wave-openclaw-wrapper. Use when the user asks about MR lists, specific MR details, MR status, wants to find MRs by author/branch/keyword, create new MRs, or shares a GitLab MR link (platgit.mihoyo.com). Covers listing, filtering, viewing MR details, and creating MRs.\\n---\\n\\n# GitLab MR Management\\n\\nManage merge requests from platgit.mihoyo.com. 支持项目：stellar-fe、wave-openclaw-wrapper。\\n\\n## Script\\n\\n`scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs` — Node.js CLI tool，配置来自 `skills/gitlab-mr/config/gitlab.json`。\\n\\n### List MRs\\n\\n```bash\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs --list [--project stellar-fe|wave-openclaw-wrapper] [options]\\n```\\n\\nOptions:\\n| Flag | Example | Notes |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `--project` | `wave-openclaw-wrapper` | 默认 stellar-fe |\\n| `--state` | `opened\\\\|merged\\\\|closed\\\\|all` | Default: opened |\\n| `--author` | `mingyuan.yang` | GitLab username |\\n| `--target` | `develop` | Target branch |\\n| `--source` | `feat/1.28_md` | Source branch |\\n| `--search` | `日历` | Keyword search |\\n| `--labels` | `bug,frontend` | Comma-separated |\\n| `--limit` | `20` | Default: 20 |\\n| `--order_by` | `created_at\\\\|updated_at` | Default: updated_at |\\n| `--sort` | `asc\\\\|desc` | Default: desc |\\n\\n### Single MR Detail\\n\\n```bash\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs <mr_iid>\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs <gitlab_mr_url>\\n```\\n\\nAccepts MR IID (e.g. `24582`) or full URL.\\n\\n### Create MR\\n\\n```bash\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs --create \\\\\\n  --source <源分支> \\\\\\n  --target <目标分支> \\\\\\n  --title <标题> \\\\\\n  [options]\\n```\\n\\nRequired flags:\\n| Flag | Example | Notes |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `--source` | `bot/xiaogang-bot/fix/3013229_xxx` | 源分支名 |\\n| `--target` | `feat/1.29_aiqa` 或 `develop` | 目标分支名 |\\n| `--title` | `fix: --bug=3013229 三击无响应` | MR 标题 |\\n\\nOptional flags:\\n| Flag | Example | Notes |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `--project` | `wave-openclaw-wrapper` | 默认 stellar-fe |\\n| `--description` | `\\\"修复三击无响应的 Bug\\\"` | MR 描述 |\\n| `--labels` | `1.29` 或 `bug,frontend` | 标签，逗号分隔 |\\n| `--assignee_ids` | `970` | 指派人 ID，逗号分隔 |\\n| `--reviewer_ids` | `970,1005` | 审核人 ID，逗号分隔 (马达=970, 黄晓刚=1005) |\\n| `--milestone_id` | `123` | 里程碑 ID |\\n| `--remove_source_branch` | `true\\\\|false` | 合并后删除源分支 |\\n| `--squash` | `true\\\\|false` | 合并时压缩提交 |\\n| `--draft` | `true\\\\|false` | 标记为草稿 |\\n\\nExample:\\n```bash\\n# stellar-fe bug fix MR\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs --create \\\\\\n  --source \\\"bot/xiaogang-bot/fix/3013229_triple_click\\\" \\\\\\n  --target \\\"feat/1.29_aiqa\\\" \\\\\\n  --title \\\"fix: --bug=3013229 --user=马达 三击无响应问题\\\" \\\\\\n  --description \\\"修复三击无响应的 Bug\\\" \\\\\\n  --labels \\\"1.29\\\" \\\\\\n  --reviewer_ids \\\"970,1005\\\"\\n\\n# wave-openclaw-wrapper feature MR\\nnode scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs --create \\\\\\n  --project wave-openclaw-wrapper \\\\\\n  --source \\\"bot/xiaogang-bot/feat/git_mr_create\\\" \\\\\\n  --target \\\"main\\\" \\\\\\n  --title \\\"feat: 添加 GitLab MR 创建功能\\\" \\\\\\n  --reviewer_ids \\\"970,1005\\\"\\n```\\n\\n## Git Commit 身份\\n\\n向 stellar-fe 仓库提交代码时，**必须**使用以下身份，不得使用任何真人的名字：\\n\\n```\\ngit config user.name \\\"wave前端龙虾\\\"\\ngit config user.email \\\"wave-fe-lobster@bot.noreply\\\"\\n```\\n\\n如果 commit 已经用了错误的身份，用 `--amend --author` 修正后 force push。\\n\\n## Auth\\n\\nToken 与 projectId 来自 `skills/gitlab-mr/config/gitlab.json`（见 `config/README.md`）。可被环境变量覆盖。\\n\\n## Tips\\n\\n- List all open MRs: `--list`\\n- Find someone's MRs: `--list --author dehai.wei`\\n- MRs targeting a branch: `--list --target develop`\\n- Recently merged: `--list --state merged --limit 10`\\n- Search by keyword: `--list --search 日历`\\n- Create MR after pushing code: `--create --source <branch> --target <base> --title \\\"<title>\\\" --reviewer_ids \\\"970,1005\\\"`\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1773777676312},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"现在查一下超期 MR：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"toolu_bdrk_01SZmMZD5kPTiuVecN5HJ9tM\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"cd /Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper && node scripts/gitlab-mr.mjs --list --project wave-openclaw-wrapper --state opened --limit 20 2>&1\",\"timeout\":30}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"museai\",\"model\":\"mihoyo.claude-4-6-opus\",\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773777676313},{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"toolu_bdrk_01SZmMZD5kPTiuVecN5HJ9