            "data": "{\"type\":\"res\",\"id\":\"2621e912-2f1e-4169-8b7a-dfa67ccfe718\",\"ok\":true,\"payload\":{\"workspaceDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/.runtime/home/.openclaw/workspace\",\"managedSkillsDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/.runtime/home/.openclaw/skills\",\"skills\":[{\"name\":\"ai-bugfix\",\"description\":\"AI 辅助修复 TAPD Bug 的完整流程。当用户提供 TAPD Bug 链接或 Bug ID 并要求修复时使用。覆盖：分析 Bug → 定位代码 → 编写修复 → 提交并推送 → 创建 MR → 推送结果消息。适用于 stellar-fe 和 wave-openclaw-wrapper 仓库。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/ai-bugfix/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/ai-bugfix\",\"skillKey\":\"ai-bugfix\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"auto-bugfix-pipeline\",\"description\":\"TAPD Bug 自动监听 & AI 辅助修复流水线（Phase 1-3）。 两种触发路径： 1. 群聊 oc_db6088bcab3f480cc32fb2b516e53f8e 收到 TAPD bot 卡片消息 → 自动触发 2. 任意会话 @bot + TAPD Bug 链接 → 手动触发 Phase 1：解析 → 过滤 → 匹配 → 去重 → 通知 Phase 2：AI 分析 → 推送分析结果 → 用户确认 Phase 3：自动修复 → 创建 MR → 复盘反馈收集 NOT for: 普通群聊消息、非 TAPD bot 消息、非 Bug 卡片。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/auto-bugfix-pipeline/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/auto-bugfix-pipeline\",\"skillKey\":\"auto-bugfix-pipeline\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"browser-context-logger\",\"description\":\"Log browser extension session context. Use when the inbound message contains browser page context (URL, page title, or page body text injected by the Cooperator Chrome extension). Triggers on any message that includes「当前站点」or「页面正文」or「当前可用工具」sections in the group chat context. NOT for plain Wave chat messages without page context.\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/browser-context-logger/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/browser-context-logger\",\"skillKey\":\"browser-context-logger\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"daily-ai-news\",\"description\":\"每日 AI 新闻摘要推送。每天搜索 AI 领域最新动态（工程应用、大模型性价比、AI 社区反馈等），整理成团队友好的中文摘要。由 cron job 每天 10:00 自动触发，也可手动调用。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/daily-ai-news/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/daily-ai-news\",\"skillKey\":\"daily-ai-news\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"git-workflow\",\"description\":\"wave-openclaw-wrapper、stellar-fe 代码变更：worktree → 编码 → MR。含分支嗅探、worktree 管理、未合并分支扫描。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/git-workflow/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/git-workflow\",\"skillKey\":\"git-workflow\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"gitlab-mr\",\"description\":\"Manage GitLab merge requests for stellar-fe or wave-openclaw-wrapper. Use when the user asks about MR lists, specific MR details, MR status, wants to find MRs by author/branch/keyword, create new MRs, or shares a GitLab MR link (platgit.mihoyo.com). Covers listing, filtering, viewing MR details, and creating MRs.\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/gitlab-mr/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/gitlab-mr\",\"skillKey\":\"gitlab-mr\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"iteration-bug-review\",\"description\":\"迭代 Bug Review 分析工具。当用户提到「迭代分析」「Bug Review」「迭代报表」或给出迭代版本号（如 1.27、1.28）要求分析 Bug 质量数据时使用。自动拉取目标迭代及前两个对比迭代的 TAPD Bug 数据，生成多维度对比分析报表，涵盖：各平台横向对比、跨迭代趋势、线上问题/重新打开/冒烟/新引入/偶现等关键指标、需求模块维度、开发人员维度、严重程度/状态/缺陷类型分布、综合结论。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/iteration-bug-review/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/iteration-bug-review\",\"skillKey\":\"iteration-bug-review\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"km-docs\",\"description\":\"Query KM (Knowledge Management) documents from the Wave project workspace. Use when the user asks about KM docs, shares a KM link (km.mihoyo.com), wants to read a specific document, search docs by keyword, or list documents under a directory. Covers reading article details, searching by title, and listing document trees.\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/km-docs/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/km-docs\",\"skillKey\":\"km-docs\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"pre-modification-check\",\"description\":\"修改 wave-openclaw-wrapper 或 stellar-fe 前必执行。edit 前：输出决策块 + worktree 检查。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/pre-modification-check/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/pre-modification-check\",\"skillKey\":\"pre-modification-check\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"tapd-bug\",\"description\":\"Query and display TAPD bug/story/task details for the Wave IM frontend team. Use when the user shares a TAPD link (tapd.cn), asks about a specific bug/story/task by ID, requests a list/summary filtered by status/owner/platform/date, asks about someone's tasks or stories, or asks anything about TAPD items in the Wave workspace. Covers bugs, stories (需求), and tasks (任务).\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/tapd-bug/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/tapd-bug\",\"skillKey\":\"tapd-bug\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"update-code\",\"description\":\"更新代码并生成 .runtime/openclaw.generated.json。用户说「帮我更新代码」等时直接执行。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/update-code/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/update-code\",\"skillKey\":\"update-code\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[\"git\"],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-km\",\"description\":\"Wave 知识库语义搜索和文档读取。通过 KM OpenAPI 直接搜索内部知识库（如 Wave 开放平台文档）、 获取文档全文内容、浏览文档目录结构。 **任何时候用户提到\\\"搜一下知识库\\\"、\\\"查一下开放平台文档\\\"、\\\"Wave API 怎么用\\\"、 \\\"卡片消息格式是什么\\\"、\\\"找一下XX的文档\\\"、\\\"知识库里有没有XX\\\"、\\\"看一下这篇文档内容\\\"、 \\\"km.mihoyo.com 链接\\\"、\\\"开放平台文档怎么说的\\\"，都应该使用这个 skill。** 与 wave-docs skill 的区别：wave-docs 用 Wave 插件内置工具操作文档（CRUD）， 本 skill 通过独立 API 凭证做知识库**语义搜索**和**文档全文读取**， 能访问 Wave 开放平台官方文档等内部知识库。 即使用户只是问了一个 Wave API 的技术问题，也应先用本 skill 搜索开放平台文档获取权威信息。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/wave-km/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/wave-km\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-km\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"weekly-fe-report\",\"description\":\"每周前端团队周报。统计本周 stellar-fe 仓库的 MR 贡献情况和 TAPD Bug 修复情况，按多维度生成分析报表。由 cron job 每周五 17:00 自动触发，也可手动调用。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/weekly-fe-report/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/skills/weekly-fe-report\",\"skillKey\":\"weekly-fe-report\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-calendar\",\"description\":\"Wave 日历管理与日程安排。**任何时候用户提到日历、日程、会议安排、查看时间表、添加事件、预约时间、循环活动、团建安排,或者询问\\\"今天有什么安排\\\"、\\\"明天几点开会\\\"、\\\"帮我约个时间\\\"时,都应该使用这个 skill。** 覆盖创建/查询/更新/取消日历事件、获取日历列表、批量操作、循环事件等完整日历管理能力。即使用户没有明确说\\\"日历\\\",只要涉及时间规划和会议安排,就应该触发本 skill。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-calendar/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-calendar\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-calendar\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-chat-history\",\"description\":\"Wave 聊天历史记录获取 - 获取群聊或单聊中的历史消息记录。 需要应用开启 im:msg:history 权限，群聊还需要群主授权。 **当用户提到\\\"查看聊天记录\\\"、\\\"群里之前说了什么\\\"、\\\"回看消息\\\"、 \\\"获取历史消息\\\"、\\\"查看上下文\\\"时，使用这个 skill。**\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-chat-history/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-chat-history\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-chat-history\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-config\",\"description\":\"Wave 扩展配置、多账号管理、环境切换、安全策略。**任何时候用户询问 Wave 插件配置方法、account_id 参数含义、如何切换测试/生产环境、群组/私聊权限设置、如何获取 appId/appSecret、或者想知道有哪些 Wave 工具可用时,都应该触发这个 skill。** 即使用户只是说\\\"Wave 怎么配置\\\"、\\\"多账号怎么用\\\"、\\\"有哪些 Wave 能力\\\",也要使用本 skill。这是所有其他 Wave skills 的配置基础。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-config/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-config\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-config\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-contacts\",\"description\":\"Wave 通讯录与用户查询。**任何时候用户询问\\\"这个人是谁\\\"、\\\"查一下某某的信息\\\"、\\\"部门有多少人\\\"、\\\"user_id 是什么\\\"、\\\"union_id 怎么转换\\\"、\\\"列出工程部成员\\\"、\\\"找他的上级\\\",都应该使用这个 skill。** 即使用户只是提到一个 user_id 或 union_id,也要考虑用本 skill 查询详细信息。覆盖用户查询、部门成员、ID转换、部门查询等通讯录能力。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-contacts/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-contacts\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-contacts\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-docs\",\"description\":\"Wave 文档与知识库操作。**任何时候用户提到\\\"创建文档\\\"、\\\"写个 Markdown\\\"、\\\"搜索文档\\\"、\\\"更新文档\\\"、\\\"删除文档\\\"、\\\"导入文档\\\"、\\\"查看子文档\\\"、\\\"创建表格\\\"、\\\"更新表格\\\"、\\\"导出表格\\\"、\\\"添加工作表\\\"、\\\"检索知识库\\\",都应该使用这个 skill。** 即使用户只是说\\\"帮我建个文档记录这个\\\"或\\\"搜一下知识库里的XX内容\\\"或\\\"做个表格\\\",也要触发本 skill。覆盖文档创建/编辑/检索、表格操作、Unravel 文档、权限查询等完整文档能力。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-docs/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-docs\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-docs\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-file-msg\",\"description\":\"Wave 文件与图片消息发送。**当用户说\\\"发个文件给他\\\"、\\\"把这张图发过去\\\"、\\\"以文件形式发送\\\"、\\\"发个图片消息\\\"、\\\"发附件\\\"、\\\"原生图片/文件消息\\\"、\\\"file_key/image_key 怎么用\\\"(不是 markdown 里的图片链接),都应该使用这个 skill。**\\n首选方式：`wave_upload_file`/`wave_upload_image` 上传拿到 key，然后直接通过 `wave_send_message`/`wave_reply_message` 的 image_key/file_key 参数发送。\\n备选方式：使用 `scripts/wave-send-file.mjs` 脚本（适用于需要指定自定义凭证或环境的场景）。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-file-msg/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-file-msg\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-file-msg\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-groups\",\"description\":\"Wave 群组管理与群聊操作。**任何时候用户提到\\\"建个群\\\"、\\\"拉个群\\\"、\\\"加人到群\\\"、\\\"踢人\\\"、\\\"解散群\\\"、\\\"改群名\\\"、\\\"设置群公告\\\"、\\\"转让群主\\\"、\\\"设置管理员\\\"、\\\"查看群成员\\\"、\\\"我在哪些群里\\\",都应该使用这个 skill。** 即使用户只是说\\\"拉上张三李四建个讨论组\\\"或\\\"把这个人踢出群\\\",也要触发本 skill。覆盖群聊创建、成员管理、群设置、权限配置、公告管理等完整群组能力。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-groups/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-groups\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-groups\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-messaging\",\"description\":\"Wave 消息发送、接收、管理。**任何时候用户提到发消息、回复、撤回、查看消息、批量通知、上传文件/图片、标记已读、获取表情反应、更新卡片、发通知时,都应该使用这个 skill。** 即使用户只是说\\\"发个消息给某某\\\"、\\\"撤回刚才那条\\\"、\\\"这条消息谁点赞了\\\"、\\\"批量通知大家\\\",也要触发本 skill。覆盖所有 Wave 消息相关操作的核心能力。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-messaging/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-messaging\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-messaging\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-minutes\",\"description\":\"Wave 会议纪要与转写。**当用户询问\\\"有哪些会议记录\\\"、\\\"查看某个会议的纪要\\\"、\\\"会议转写\\\"、\\\"会上说了什么\\\"、\\\"总结一下会议内容\\\"、\\\"找一下XXX会议的记录\\\",都应该使用这个 skill。** 即使用户只是说\\\"看看昨天的会\\\"或\\\"那个项目评审会说了啥\\\",也要触发本 skill。覆盖会议纪要列表查询和转写内容获取能力。\\n\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-minutes/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-minutes\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-minutes\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"wave-sdk\",\"description\":\"Wave JS SDK (@mihoyo/wave-opensdk) 完整 API 参考与插件代码架构。 **任何时候需要查看 Wave SDK 方法签名、参数类型、返回类型、调用方式时使用。** 覆盖：消息（send/reply/recall/get/updateCard/streaming）、群组（create/members/config）、 通讯录（getUsers/convertIds/departments）、日历（CRUD events，需 user_token）、 文档（document/markdown/spreadsheet/unravel）、文件上传、认证（OAuth/user_token）、 会议纪要等全部 SDK 模块。 当遇到以下场景时触发： - 需要确认某个 API 的确切参数名或类型 - 写新的 Wave API 调用代码 - 排查 API 调用失败（retcode 错误码） - 理解 SDK 内部行为（token 管理、请求链路、错误处理） - 修改插件中的 SDK 调用逻辑 - 需要知道某个 API 对应的 Path 枚举值 即使只是一个简单的\\\"这个 API 怎么调\\\"的问题，也应该使用本 skill 查证后再回答。\",\"source\":\"openclaw-extra\",\"bundled\":false,\"filePath\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-sdk/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/Users/xiaogang.h/work/wave-fe/ai-调研/claw-sources/wave-openclaw-wrapper/vendor/openclaw-wave-extension/skills/wave-sdk\",\"skillKey\":\"wave-sdk\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":true,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[]},{\"name\":\"1password\",\"description\":\"Set up and use 1Password CLI (op). Use when installing the CLI, enabling desktop app integration, signing in (single or multi-account), or reading/injecting/running secrets via op.\",\"source\":\"openclaw-bundled\",\"bundled\":true,\"filePath\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/1password/SKILL.md\",\"baseDir\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/1password\",\"skillKey\":\"1password\",\"emoji\":\"🔐\",\"homepage\":\"https://developer.1password.com/docs/cli/get-started/\",\"always\":false,\"disabled\":false,\"blockedByAllowlist\":false,\"eligible\":false,\"requirements\":{\"bins\":[\"op\"],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"missing\":{\"bins\":[\"op\"],\"anyBins\":[],\"env\":[],\"config\":[],\"os\":[]},\"configChecks\":[],\"install\":[{\"id\":\"brew\